\q1 Ani aiqama naamuaqira ufauqa naaruara marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 152 Qinee ooqai ani naakapara ufa iriqiafana.
\q1 Mi ufausa anee qunaqa naaru marira ufauqaika mafiqau.
\q1 
\v 153 Qini aupurarana qafamasee minakinaana qini maraqisaa.
\q1 Qinee sia ani sandufa qaununnanara miqimma qisaa.
\q1 
\v 154 Qinee ufaki marunnana ititaqimaqasee qini idukuqisaa.
\q1 Anee aneenna qima afeekaikunandee inana qini amiqiraqoo mara quqaqisaa.
\q1 
\v 155 Manda oosana maree mariasa misa ani sanda ufa mau sia fimariasa anee sia mareeqee amiqira qoo quqanniseennaranoo.
\q1 
\v 156 Miqi mariafana oo Yaawee anee qiniara amudaaoo qirafa firaaqoo marinara aneenna nifauarana uqaqifiqasee mareeqee amiqiraqoo quqaqisaa.
\q1 
\v 157 Qini namuqaauqa ummaara qimi mariasa moomoo maridaqa.
\q1 Misa miqiqa mariafaqa qinee sia ani sandufasaaqari quandaki moosaa fiqa kaqi mi mau kai fidaqa.
\q1 
\v 158 Ani sanda ufa minnisee ueeqee mariasa qinee niqafamasee fidiaqaamma nimaqaidaqa.
\q1 Sia ani naamuaqira ufa mau fimarianara miqidaqa.
\q1 
\v 159 Oo Yaawee doo qafaa, ani naakapara ufara firaaqoo dididanoo.
\q1 Ani aidirafa sia moosaa fimarinara mariqoo kai marinara qini marirana afeedamma qisaa.
\q1 
\v 160 Ani sanda ufa oosana anoona maridanoo.
\q1 Marifanoo ani aiqama andeeqara rainannimaqara ufafa naaru naaru marirafa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 161 Misa faiqí uriqararausa misa fifau qini mandaikamma qimaqaidaqa.
\q1 Misa miqi mariafaqa qinee ani sanda ufara kai qeerairammasee qaindusidaqa.
\q1 
\v 162 Qinee ani qima afeekaikira ufara firaaqoo asasidaqa.
\q1 Mee faiqí moo fannoo koorara paqurimmasee asasindee qinee faqa miqi kai masee ani ufara asasidaqa.
\q1 
\v 163 Qinee aiqama unna ufara qikooqeenoo fidiaqaa uqanna qidaqa.
\q1 Miqi marunanoo ani sanda ufara kai dididanoo.
\q1 
\v 164 Qinee aiqama faasaana moodaanai qisauku taikasee dinni oonu qaaraqanda marasee kari ani andeeqara rainannimaqaranara dufi dufi qimamaqaidaqa.
\q1 
\v 165 Ani sandufara nidi marisa asooaranaki maridaqa.
\q1 Sia moo ainaina fannoo nikuama niminaqa saamurifaranoo.
\q1 
\v 166 Oo Yaawee anee qini asumu mara qisaanneera afeesidaqa anee daamuaqianna mau kai fidaqa.
\q1 
\v 167 Qinee ani naakapara ufa mau fidaqa.
\q1 Qinee qeeqa aiqama qimuqusannoo minara dididanoo.
\q1 
\v 168 Qinee ani naamuaqira ufa faqa ani naakapara ufa mau fidaqa.
\q1 Qinee aiqama ainaina auqee marunnana anee qafee mariananoo.
\q1 
\v 169 Oo Yaawee qini nammeera qirafa anee iannannai oorufuani.
\q1 Aneenna qima afeekaikunandee inana irirana oosana qimia.
\q1 
\v 170 Qini innaaruqirana irisee aneenna qima afeekaikammaqoonnana amana kai mara amiqira qoo quqaqisaa.
\q1 
\v 171 Anee aneenna sanda ufa qima qimiannanara qinee aiqama kari ani amooqianaura.
\q1 
\v 172 Ani naamuaqira ufa aiqamausa andeeqasee raina nimaqee marifa marinara ani sanda ufara idi raanaura.
\q1 
\v 173 Qinee ani naamuaqira ufa afaqee marunnanara aiqama kari qini dadaaqirara deedaqina maria.
\q1 
\v 174 Oo Yaawee qinee ummaaraki marunnanara firaaqoo ani afeedamma qimaqaranara rakisidaqa.
\q1 Qinee asasirana ani sandufaki paquridaqa.
\q1 
\v 175 Anee maqee marirana qiminaqa amana qinee ani amooqianaura.
\q1 Ani naakapara ufa fannoo qini dadaaqamma qimaqaani
\q1 
\v 176 Qinee auiara sipsipara foora auiaqa nidaqa.
\q1 Qinee sia ani sandufa qimeesu uqimarunnanara anee aniree qini aneenna ainainira faiqi randasee paquria.
\c 120
\s1 Dadaaqiani fee innaaru.
\q1 
\v 1 Qinee manda ummaaraki maridaqa Yaaweena aaraunanoo mifa eedoo qimasee dadaaqinoo.
\q1 
\v 2 Oo Yaawee unnaqimariasa faqa ueeqee mariasa faqa nisaukukinaana mareeqee kaqinni quqaqisaa.
\q1 
\v 3 Innee unna qimariasa Anutufa inni naqaa fee mannimaqaannoo.
\q1 Mifa naqimmaseenoo fee inni aupurarana nimiannoo fee.
\q1 
\v 4 Sundia rakira feefannoo faqa fidika arira idaurunnai faqa naruannoo.
\q1 
\v 5 Inni qambaanai marirafa kaasau maqannaa aamina maqannaasa qambaanara foora mandaikiqa maridaqa.
\q1 
\v 6 Qinee asooaranara fidiaqaa imariasaki kisaaqasaa uqanna mariaafanausa maridaqa.
\q1 
\v 7 Qinee asooaranara qimarunaqa misa rakiranara kai qidaqa.
\c 121
\s1 Yaaweefa maasa itita qimaqee marifa.
\q1 
\v 1 Qinee aaqanai qifu maqasee, qini dadaaqirafa yaindari fee aniannoo fee qidaqa.
\q1 
\v 2 Qini dadaaqirafa Yaawee finaindari kai aniannoo.
\q1 Maa maqana faqa innaaruna faqa auqu quqoo finnaindari kai aniannoo.
\q1 
\v 3 Mifa sia aniara qinana aqufinnaranoo.
\q1 Ani rakisi amaqee marifa aiqama kari afu maqaida maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 4 Isaraee maqannaasasaa rakisinnimaqee marifa sia moo kari qaunduarinoo sia faiqaidannoo.
\q1 
\v 5 Yaaweefa ani rakisi amaqaannoo.
\q1 Mifa ani itita amaqarara ani aaqa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 6 Suani fannoo faasaana sia naruannoo.
\q1 Kafaa eendaki quqoona fannoo sia naruannoo.
\q1 
\v 7 Yaaweefa aiqama mandainainaki innisaa ititamma nimaqaannoo.
\q1 Mifa inni nariranasaa itita nimaqasee innisaa rakisiannoo.
\q1 
\v 8 Mifa kai inni firannai anirannaira rakisi nimaqaannoo.
\q1 Maqee faqa naaru naaru faqa rakisi nimaqaannoo.
\c 122
\s1 Yeerusaree maqusa amooqia.
\q1 
\v 1 Yaaweena amaana maaqai firaree qimasee qimaqimiafaqa qinee asasiqa.
\q1 
\v 2 Maqee maasa maaqoo Yeerusaree faandaamura kooqiki keeqafi afuqaki maridaqa.
\q1 
\v 3 Yeerusaree maqusa usakasoofanoo kaaqa amiqirafa atiuqa amana amana kai inoo maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 4 Isaraeena akeeku akaaku miqimmasee aniree Yaaweena naamuaqira ufa amana kai dufi dufi qirana amidaqa.
\q1 
\v 5 Maaqoo Yeerusaree maqannaa karaambaiqauqa nariqa faiqí anaasee ufa andeeqa nimaqararee qimasee ooqu mariqau.
\q1 
\v 6 Yeerusaree maqusa asooaranaki marianifeera innaaruqiaqa.
\q1 Yeerusaree maqusara rimariasa aiqama ainaina rairaa iani
\q1 
\v 7 Oo Yeerusaree maqusa ani faandaamura afuqaki asooarafa kai mariani.
\q1 Ani karaambaiqauqa nári maaqaki amiqimmasee mariaqa.
\q1 
\v 8 Qeeqa ainainara faqa qeeqa qiqoondiuqara faqa irisee Yeerusaree maqusara maaqi qidaqa.
\q1 Asooarafa aniki mariani.
\q1 
\v 9 Yaaweena maasa Anutuna amaana maaqara irisee inni Yeerusaree maqannaasee irairaamma nimaqaranara innaaru qidaqa.
\q1 Anutufa qimudaoo qirana amiani fee innaaru.
\c 123
\q1 
\v 1 Oo Yaawee qinee anee iannannai qifu maqaidaqa.
\q1 Innaarunai anee rakisi nimaqee mariannannai qifu maqasee dadaaqianneera innaaru qidaqa.
\q1 
\v 2 Ainainira faiqi nariqa rakisiranasaa nifu mundi mariandee iqa kafaa faqa ainainira maanaaqa miqikai inoo narí rakisira aanaaseesaa mundidanoo.
\q1 Oo Yaawee maasa Anutufa maasa miqi kai iqa ani qafaqa maridaqa anee maasara qimudaoo qirana qimianneera afeesidaqa.
\q1 
\v 3 Oo Yaawee maasara qimudaoo qimasee qifauama qimaqaa.
\q1 Maasa moomoo aasaandaana ufa qima qimaqaidaqa.
\q1 
\v 4 Ainaina faqaasa kisaaqasaa maasara uteeti qidaqa.
\q1 Kafaa nári nimoo qimariasa nári mara maree uriranannai maasa rafaaqafusee ataasa ataasa qima qimaqaidaqa.
\c 124
\s1 Anutufa narí faiqí anaasee itita nimaqee marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 1 Yaaweefa maasa sia dadaaqinaqau naqaa fee unaiqini.
\q1 Oo Isaraee maqannaasa minara qima qimifaqa iria.
\q1 
\v 2-3 Yaaweefa maasa sia dadaaqinaqau namuqaa nári aanoo qiranannai maasa qumarasee kaqi kasi marunaqa nambiqaa qini.
\q1 
\v 4 Miqinanoofau nammari aufirafa maasa maree fiqini.
\q1 Kaifaa nammari maasa rafaaqafu qisaiqini.
\q1 
\v 5 Nammari aufinoo firaaqoo aiai qimarifa maasa ukuqnama qimaqaiqini.
\q1 
\v 6 Yaaweefa maasa namuqaara qifaqa sia maasa mandaikamma qimaqaanara maasa mina dufi dufi qimamaqaa.
\q1 
\v 7 Maasa ufiniara foora faiqí ufini ufanaki arurudukaki fiara foommiqa.
\q1 Mi fasiqana ufaana raudafifaqa maasa qifaaqa quqasee mana mana idaqa.
\q1 
\v 8 Maasa dadaaqirafa Yaawee finnaindari anidanoo.
\q1 Maqa faqa innaaruna faqa auqu finnaindari anidanoo.
\c 125
\s1 Anutuna faiqí aanaaseesa rakisirafa.
\q1 
\v 1 Yaaweena saqariki mariasa Sioona aaqanara foora maridaqa.
\q1 Sia amana kasi annoo sia moo fannoo mina mareeqee moosaa quqaannoo.
\q1 
\v 2 Aaqanauqa Yeerusaree maqusa fiqu fiqumma datinoo marindee inoo Yaaweefa narí faiqí anaasee fiqu fiqumma ititannimaqasee maqee faqa naaru faqa rakisi nimaqaidanoo.
\q1 
\v 3 Mandoosana maree mariasa sia amana andeeqarausa maqasaa aiqama kari rakisifaranoo.
\q1 Misa miqifaqa andeeqarausa misasaaqaraa aaqara oosana maree foora.
\q1 
\v 4 Oo Yaawee andeeqara oosana maree mariasa amiqi amiqimmannimaqaa.
\q1 Ani naamuaqira ufamau fimariasa amiqi amiqimma nimaqaa.
\q1 
\v 5 Miqidana anee manda oosana maree mariasa aupurarana nimidana ani ufa minnisee kaqi runna fimariasa faqa aupurarana nimia.
\q1 Asooarafa Isaraee maqannaaki mariani.
\q1 Manda ainainakinaana mara kaqinni uqannisaani fee innaaru.
\c 126
\q1 
\v 1 Yaaweefa maasa Yeerusareenni qifiqee anufa qainasaara foora marinau.
\q1 
\v 2 Maasa firaaqoo naanaidara qida asasida idiree mariqau.
\q1 Miqi mariafanaqa akaqa maqannaasa maasara maaqi qiqau.
\q1 Yaaweefa firaa ainaina dadaaqinoo fee qiqau.
\q1 
\v 3 Kuqaa mifa firaa ainaina maasa dadaaqufaqa maasa minara firaaqoo asasiqiafana.
\q1 
\v 4 Aadaturunna aaku rifanoo nammari qumi marindee inana kaifaa maasa amiqi amiqimma qimaqaa.
\q1 
\v 5 Naukuna namu faqa ummaqi mariasa asasira idi namu faqa unakuaqanani.
\q1 
\v 6 Asumu ainaina ummaqiraree qimasee naukunu namufaqa maree munu ummaqusee mariifaqa nara aukuana unaku maree asasira idi namu faqa maree anifaranoo.
\c 127
\s1 Anutuna amiqira oosana amooqia.
\q1 
\v 1 Yaaweefa sia maaqa usakaifanoo, usakara saika fannoo anoona siaifa mariqini.
\q1 Yaaweefa sia maqusasaa ititee marifanoo aufari mari fasiqafa kikiqinoo marida rakisi mari oosanafa sia amanaikiqini.
\q1 
\v 2 Fifau kananaana eendai uqanna findifi ainaina kadaapirina fifiina eendi mariananoo.
\q1 Yaaweefa narí aidi marisa faiqaqee iafanoo narana nimidanoo.
\q1 
\v 3 Faiqi asumu Yaaweefa kaqi nimi mari ainainafa maridanoo.
\q1 Mifa kaaqa afaaramasee amiqi amiqimma qimaqaidanoo.
\q1 
\v 4 Kumaaraasaa maqainna faiqisa nári nikoona asaukuki rakira fasiqauqa duru feefara foora maridaqa.
\q1 
\v 5 Miqira fasiqa moomoo faiqi duru feefara foora mina asaukuki karariqa mariafanoo asasidanoo.
\q1 Mifa ufa iriranaki mina namuqaauqa sia mina rafaaqa fifaranoo.
\c 128
\s1 Yaaweena ufa qaindusi mariana akiiqara nimirafa.
\q1 
\v 1 Yaaweena ufamau fimariasa asasidaqa.
\q1 Mina naamuaqira ufasaa mariasa faqa asasidaqa.
\q1 
\v 2 Anee miqi marianafa aiqama kari ani kadaapirirafa narana ainaina amiannoo.
\q1 Ani ainaina reemindeemirinoo marinana asasinnarannoo.
\q1 
\v 3 Ani anaaqa fannoo wainna sandara foora maaqaki mariranaki moomoo qaqama iraannoo.
\q1 Ani akoonaiqi faiqiuqa oorifa amiqira saqariara foora ani narana nee marianna difaanina fiqu fiquiqa marifaranoo.
\q1 
\v 4 Faiqí Yaaweena ufamau fimarifa miqimmaseenoo kaaqa amiqi amiqiannoo.
\q1 
\v 5 Yaaweefa Sioonna maqusakiqari inni amiqi amiqimma nimaqaani.
\q1 Inneeqa kaqi marinna kamu Yeerusaree maqusaki aiqama ainaina reemindee mirirana qafaaqanani.
\q1 
\v 6 Innee kisaaqasaa marida inneeqa ninaiqimara niqafaaqanani.
\q1 Asooarafa Isaraee maqannaasaki mariani.
\c 129
\s1 Isaraee maqannaasa nariqa namuqaauqa mandaikamma nimaqaani fee innaaru qiqau.
\q1 
\v 1 Innee Isaraee maqannaasa innee kumaaraasaa maruqooqari inni namuqaa ummaara nimi maree ani marianara qima qimiaqa.
\q1 
\v 2 Qinee kumaaraa mariafannaqooqari qini namuqaauqa niranaqee marufaqa qini mandaikamma qimaqee mariqau.
\q1 Miqidaqa sia qini uridaaqaree mariqau.
\q1 
\v 3 Maqarumasee afuqaki oora ateekee mariandee iqa namuqaauqa qini kaakadi qitaufaka runna oorara foora meemai uqanna ateekee mariqau.
\q1 
\v 4 Miqi marufanoo Yaaweefa andeeqarafa maridanoo rumbaranakinaana iduku qisanau.
\q1 
\v 5 Aiqama Sioonna maqusara fidiaqaa imariasa rafaaqa fusaifaqa anirandeeqa sandeefarannoo.
\q1 
\v 6 Misa maaqasaa ururee mari andanda fara foora urureenoo aadana usidanoo.
\q1 
\v 7 Sia moo fannoo mina suqu moodaanaki quqaidaqa sia rumbamaree fidaqa.
\q1 
\v 8 Aiqaree fimariasakiqari sia moo fannoo Yaaweefa amiqi amiqimma amaqaanifee qifaranoo.
\q1 Maasa Yaaweena auqusaa amiqi amiqimma amaqaidee qidaqa.
\c 130
\s1 Dadaaqiani fee innaaru.
\q1 
\v 1 Qini qimuqusa mandaikirafa faruma uqnauriara foora inoo marifaqa oo Yaawee qinee ani innaaru kiqari aaraidaqa.
\q1 
\v 2 Oo Yaawee anee qini nameera qirana iria.
\q1 Anee aaqoo rammatinimmaseenana qini qiki raqarana iriseenana dadaaqia.
\q1 
\v 3 Oo Yaawee anee maasa aaqarana papiqaki kaqi akara rumasaina marinanoo yafee ani ufa nimiranaki fiqaraannoo.
\q1 
\v 4 Maasara aneenna afusaa naaquqamasee mariaqeera maasa manda oosana akiiqara minninnisee marianafa mariananoo.
\q1 
\v 5 Qinee Yaaweena dadaaqiranara asasida afeesidaqa. Mina ufa saqarikidaqa.
\q1 
\v 6 Qinee Yaaweena dadaaqiranara asasida afeesi marunafa aufari maria fasiqausa suani afu uriranara rakisi mariana uraaqaranoo maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 7 Yaaweena sia taikaaninna amuqusirafa marinara faqa mifa maasa mandainainakinaana dadaaqirara aidi marinara faqa irisee, Isaraee maqannaasa Yaaweena saqarikiaqa.
\q1 
\v 8 Mifa narí faiqí anaasee Isaraee maqannaasa nári aiqama aaqaranakinaana dadaaqiannoo.
\c 131
\s1 Anutuna saqarikammasee innaaru qira oosana.
\q1 
\v 1 Oo Yaawee qinee qeeqa qimooqirana minniseeqa.
\q1 Qeeqa ramoo ramaa irana faqa minnisee qimeesa uquseeqa.
\q1 Qinee sia firaa ainainauqara oonu mafi iridaqa, qinee sia amanaiki marunna ainainara faqa sia iridaqa.
\q1 
\v 2 Qinee sia miqidaqa, qinee asooaranaki qifaaqa quqasee maridaqa.
\q1 Faiqi aanaaqi nári ninausa nifundanasaa ireeda faiqaqee iandee iqa marunanoo qini qimuqusa fannoo ireeda qiniki maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 3 Oo Isaraee maqannaasa maqee faqa naaru faqa Yaaweena kai saqari kiaqa.
\c 132
\s1 Anutuna amaana maqara amooqia.
\q1 
\v 1 Oo Yaawee anee sia Dafidinara qaunua.
\q1 Mifa oosana oosana aupurarana maroonara faqa sia qaunua.
\q1 
\v 2 Oo Yaawee Dafidifa qima afeekaikunara iria.
\q1 Mifa ani afeeka faqaa Anutuna Yakooboona Anutuna faqa qima afeekaikunara iria.
\q1 
\v 3 Qinee sia qeeqa faiqara maaqai fuanaura.
\q1 
\v 4 Qinee sia idooeeqa faiqeeqa ianauranoo.
\q1 
\v 5 Qinee afeeka faqaa Anutuna Yakooboona Anutuna maqusa deedaqammaseeqa inaaqianna faiqaanaura.
\q1 
\v 6 Maasa Beeteereeqeemma maqusaki maridaqa moodaanaki kira bookisara irisee Yeearimma afaasasaa paqurimmasee qafaqiafana.
\q1 
\v 7 Maasa maaqi qiafana. Anifaqa maasa Yaaweena amaana maqai oonuree mina ufa irira qaari oorinni oonuree amooqiaqa.
\q1 
\v 8 Oo Yaawee moodaanaki kira bookisa namu faqa mara maree aneenna naauqara uiqaana maaqaki ania.
\q1 Mi moodaanaki kira bookisafa ani afeekara kooroo imarina faqa maree aniree maaqoo naaruara maria.
\q1 
\v 9 Ani aanaiqikirausa aiqama kari andeeqara ainaina kai auqaaqanani.
\q1 Ani faiqí anaasee faaqa fuisee qidaqa asasiaqanani.
\q1 
\v 10 Oo Yaawee aneenna ainainira faiqi Dafidinara qima afeekaikinau.
\q1 Sia aneenna utaaqamaqaanna karaambaiqana minni aisaa.
\q1 
\v 11 Anee oori kandamasee Dafidinara qima afeekaikinau.
\q1 Sia kaifaa mi qima afeekaikirana rukaanauranoo fee qimasee qima afeekaikamasee maaqi qinau.
\q1 Qinee ani faiqi namukinaana moo karaambaiqaika masaananoo anee kuqu finanoo mifa Isaraee maqannaasasaa rakisiannoo.
\q1 
\v 12 Ani faiqi namu qini moodaanaki kira ufamau andeeqasee fiqa qini naamuaqira ufa nimunnana mau andeeqasee fifanoo misa faiqi namu faqa anee kuqinaqa ani amaaqa maqasee karaambaiqa marifaranoo.
\q1 
\v 13 Yaaweefa narí faiqara maaqaikianifeera Sioona maqusa utaaqanau.
\q1 
\v 14 Maaqoo qinee naaruara maridaqa rakisinnimaqaanaura.
\q1 
\v 15 Qinee Sioona maqusanaasa nidi mari ainainausa aiqama nimianaura.
\q1 Mi maqusanakinaasa kudi mariasa naranannoo amiqimma nimaqaanaura.
\q1 
\v 16 Qinee mi maqusanakina aanaiqikirausa mariasa auqainna aiqama ainainna amiqi amiqimma nisaanaqa minakinaa fasiqa anaasee asasira idi raidaqa faaqa fuisee qifaranoo.
\q1 
\v 17 Mi maqusanaki qinee Dafidina akeeku akaakukinaana afeeka karaambaiqaika masaanaura.
\q1 Mi maqusanaki qinee qeeqa utaaqamaqaunna karaambaiqana rakisinnimaqarana afeedamma aisaanaura.
\q1 
\v 18 Qinee mi karaambaiqana namuqaauqa nisauriranannoo rafaaqafu nisaanauranoo.
\q1 Mina rakisinnimaqaranaki mariasa amiqiranaki marifanoo aiqama ainaina irairaa iannoo.
\c 133
\s1 Akaqaafasaara rira oosanara aidia.
\q1 
\v 1 Anutuna faiqí anaasee moodaanaki marida narí amiqi narí amiqirafa kaaqa amiqirafa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 2 Mi amiqi amiqirafa Aaroona akiiaaqa oorifa fadameena amiqirana adiasoofanoo qumu rameeqee oosaumau qumundee ira amiqi amiqirafa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 3 Mi amiqi amiqirafa Qeeramoona aaqanasaaqaraa qifi faramu Sioona aaqanasaa aqufinoo aiqama ainaina asooama nimaqaindee idanoo.
\q1 Yaaweefa miqi qimasee narí amiqi amiqirana nimiraree qimasee qima afeekaikinau.
\q1 Mi amiqi amiqirafa kisaaqa marirafa maridanoo.
\c 134
\s1 Anutuna amooqira nameera qirafa.
\q1 
\v 1 Innee Yaaweena naaquqara amaana maqaki eendaki ainaini mariasa innee aiqama aniree Yaaweena amooqiaqa.
\q1 
\v 2 Amaana maqaki inneeqa nisauku uqeerasee innaaru qidaqa Yaaweena amooqimma amaqaaqa.
\q1 
\v 3 Yaaweefa maa maqana faqa miri innaarunna faqa auqu quqoofa Sioona maqusakiqari inni amiqi amiqimma nimaqaani.
\c 135
\s1 Anutuna amooqira idi.
\q1 
\v 1 Yaaweena amooqiaqa.
\q1 Yaaweena auqu mina ainainira faiqiuqa amooqiaqa.
\q1 
\v 2 Innee Yaaweena naaquqara amaana maqaki ainaini mariasa innee Yaaweena amooqiaqa.
\q1 
\v 3 Yaaweefa andeeqarafa marinara mina amooqima amaqaaqa.
\q1 Mifa maasara qimudaoo qimarinara mina auquara amooqira idi ramamaqaaqa.
\q1 
\v 4 Mifa nariara Yakooboona utaaqanau.
\q1 Mifa mina akeeku akaaku Isaraee maqannaa fasiqa anaasee naríndi kiaqeera utaaqanau.
\q1 
\v 5 Maasa Yaaweefa aiqama unna qira anutusa firaaqoo uriqararafa marinara iridaqa.
\q1 
\v 6 Innaaruna ameemaanai faqa maqasaa faqa ooruku nammariki faqa mina aundurai faqa Yaaweefa narí aidiranannai kai imarifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 7 Mifa narí kai qifanoo asuru nannamu ira oonamu maqa dinni atindari uridanoo.
\q1 Asukuna arira oonamuki Yaaweefa aakuasaa quqasaifanoo aaku namu faqa qumidanoo.
\q1 Mifa narí afeedira maaqaki qariara foora ufaira qifanoo uqidanoo.
\q1 
\v 8 Yaaweefa Isipa maqannaasa ooqa faiqiuqa faqa misa aandau ooqa anaaqiuqa faqa moodaa karammasee narinau.
\q1 
\v 9 Miqoo mifa misa karaambaiqa faqa misa faiqí firaasa faqa aaqarana akiiqara aupurarana nimiraree qimasee misaki faiqí sia auqaaqaa ira ainaina faqa naaquqara ainaina faqa auqanau.
\q1 
\v 10 Mifa moomoo maqannaasa mandaikamma nimaqasee misa afeeka karaambaiqauqa kuqa narinau.
\q1 
\v 11 Amoora maqannaasa karaambaiqa mina auqu Sioonana faqa Basanna maqannaasa karaambaiqa mina auqu Ookana faqa Kannaa maqannaasa karaambaiqauqa aiqama faqa kuqa narinau.
\q1 
\v 12 Naruseenoo misa maqa maaqa rafieeqeenoo narí faiqí anaasee Isaraee maqannaasa niminau.
\q1 
\v 13 Oo Yaawee faiqí anaasee aiqama kari aniara Anutu fee qimasee koorooifaranoo.
\q1 Aiqama naaru kambiqainausa aniara irifaranoo.
\q1 
\v 14 Yaaweefa narí faiqí anaasee ititannimaqasee narí ainainira faiqiuqara qimudaoo qiannoo.
\q1 
\v 15 Anaamuru mariasa misa unna qira anutusauqa koorannai faqa siruaannai faqa faiqí nisaukunnoo auquqoofauqa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 16 Misa noo aamara marifaqa sia ufa qidaqa, nifu marifaqa sia qafaidaqa.
\q1 
\v 17 Misa naaqoo marifaqa sia ufa iridaqa.
\q1 Misa naikaamaraindari sia uqanna kaqi kaaqoo naannamma naidaqa.
\q1 
\v 18 Mi unnaqira anutusa auqu quqoosa faqa mina saqariki mariasa faqa mi sia kasi mari ainainnara foora mariaqanani.
\q1 
\v 19 Oo Isaraee maqannaasa innee Yaaweena amooqiaqa.
\q1 Innee aanaiqikirausa Aaroona faiqi namu innee faqa Anutuna amooqiaqa.
\q1 
\v 20 Innee Reefina aiku asauku mariasa Yaaweena amooqiaqa.
\q1 Aiqama innee minara innaru qimariasa Yaaweena amooqiaqa.
\q1 
\v 21 Sioona maqusakiqari Yaaweena amooqiaqa.
\q1 Yaaweena amooqiaqa.
\c 136
\s1 Anutuna dufi dufi qimamaqara idi.
\q1 
\v 1 Yaaweefa andeeqarafa marinara dufi dufi qimamaqaaqa.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 2 Aiqama unnaqira anutusa uriqararana dufi dufi qimamaqaaqa.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 3 Aiqama karaambaiqauqa afeeka urinnaaqararana dufi dufi qimamaqaaqa.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 4 Mifa kai firaa naaquqara ainaina auqi marifa maridanoo.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 5 Mifa narí amiqira iriranannai innaaruna auqufa maridanoo.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 6 Mifa maa maqana auqeeqee nammari faruma amuaaqa quqanau.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 7 Mifa suani faqa quqoona faqa auqinau.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 8 Mifa suaniara anee iaqaranasaa rakisiannee qimasee auqinau.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 9 Mifa quqoona faqa fasauqara faqa eendirana saa rakisiaqee qinau.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 10 Mifa Isipa maqannaasa ooqa faiqiuqa narinau.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 11 Mifa Isaraee maqannaasa Isipa maqusaindaraana aana muqunufaqa fiqau.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 12 Mifa misa narí afeeka asaukunnai nifiqee finau.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 13 Mifa Taatuqee nammari qambaana rakeeinau.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 14 Mifa narí faiqí anaasee minaki aana muqunufaqa fiqau.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 15 Fitaqa fufanoo Isipa maqannaasa karaambaiqa narí rakira fasiqauqa faqa oonuroofanoo ukuqnama nimaqanau.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 16 Mifa narí faiqí anaasee nifu uqufaqa aadana maqa maaqaki fiqau.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 17 Mifa maqasaa afeeka faqaa karaambaiqauqa narinau.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 18 Mifa firaa nuqu faqaa karaambaiqauqa narinau.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 19 Amoora maqannaasa karaambaiqa mina auqu Siqoonnana arinau.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 20 Basanna maqannaasa karaambaiqa mina auqu Ookana faqa arinau.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 21 Yaaweefa mi maqannaaqanda maqa maaqa rafieeqeenoo narí faiqí anaasee Isaraee maqannaasa niminau.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 22 Narí ainainira faiqiuqa Isaraee maqannaasa niminau.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 23 Maasa namuqaa rafaaqafu qimaqoofanoo mifa maasara sia qauninau.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 24 Mifa maasa namuqaa rumbaranakinaana idukuqisanau.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 25 Mifa kai faiqí faqa aiqama aandau auqu rarana faqa doodaani auqu rarana faqa narana nimidanoo.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 26 Anutufa innaarunai marina dufi dufi qimamaqaaqa.
\q1 Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\c 137
\s1 Isaraee maqannaasa Babilonia maqa maaqaki maridaqa iki raqoo ufafa.
\q1 
\v 1 Maasa Yuda maqannaasa Babiroonia maqannaasa rumbaranaki maridaqa Babiroonnia nammariuqa afainni ooqufaaqee idaqa Sioonna maqusara irisaidaqa iki raqee mariqiafana.
\q1 
\v 2 Maasa miqoo maridaqa doori runusee nariqa piripunna saqari asaanasaa diri qiafana.
\q1 
\v 3 Maasa rumbaqimaqee marusa maasara qidaqa idi raaqee qiqau.
\q1 Idi raidaqa maasa asasirana qimiaqee qiqau.
\q1 Sioonna maqusara rara idi rama nimiaqee qiqau.
\q1 
\v 4 Misa miqi qufaqa maasa maaqi qiqiafana.
\q1 Maasa naqimasee fee aanaamuru maqa maaqakiaqa Yaaweena amooqira idi raanauree. Sia amana.
\q1 
\v 5 Qinee Yeerusaree maqusara qaunuseefau qinee sia kaifaa naaruara piripunna amana aruanaura.
\q1 
\v 6 Qinee ani Yeerusaree maqusara sia aiqama kari irifau sia amana kaifaa naaruara idi raanaura.
\q1 Anee qini uriqarara asasirafa mariannanara qaunusee sia amana kaifaa idi raanaura.
\q1 
\v 7 Babiroonnia maqannaasa Yeerusaree maqusa faandaamura rakeemmasee keeqoo faqa Eedoomma maqannaasa namuqaa fuki faaki qidaqa Yeerusree maqusa rapeepaa iaqeera qunara Yaawee anee iriseenana mina akiiqara ia.
\q1 Oo Yaawee anee misufara iriqaraasammasee sia qaunua.
\q1 
\v 8 Oo Babiroonnia maqannaasa innee kuridi fifaranoo.
\q1 Maasa Isaraee maqannaasa saaroo qinana Babiroonnia maqannaasa narinafa asasiannoo.
\q1 
\v 9 Inni Babiroonia maqannaasa faiqi aanaaqiuqa qumaree maasa Isaraee maqannaasa saarooqi oonisaa rutukinafa asasiannoo.
\c 138
\s1 Anutunara dufi dufi qira innaaru.
\q1 
\v 1 Oo Yaawee qinee qeeqa qimuqusa ookiqari dufi dufi qimamaqaidaqa.
\q1 Unna anutusa nifusaa ani Yaaweena amooqira idi raanaura.
\q1 
\v 2 Qinee ani naaquqara amaana maqa maritinai ubeekamafi qiqoori saunu arafi ani auqu amooqianaura.
\q1 Ani sia taikaaninna amuqusiranara faqa ani mapukusee marira oosana faqa marinara ani amooqianaura.
\q1 Anee aneenna auqu faqa aneenna naamuaqira ufa faqa aiqama ainaina urinnaaqararana uqannifiqoonnanara ani auqu amooqianaura.
\q1 
\v 3 Oo Yaawee qinee aaraunana iriseenana anee qimaqimiananoo.
\q1 Aneenna afeekannai qini afeekaikamma qimaqaananoo.
\q1 
\v 4 Aiqama maa maqa maaqanaki maria uriqararausa ani Yaaweena ufa irianara ani amooqifaranoo.
\q1 
\v 5 Misa anee auqoonna ainainara faqa ani firaa afeekara faqa irisee idi reefaranoo.
\q1 
\v 6 Anee kaaqa mirinni uriqarana maridana ureeqarausasaa rakisinimaqee mariananoo.
\q1 Faiqí nári nimoo naamoo qimariasa sia amana ani afusaaqari kukeeqeefaranoo.
\q1 
\v 7 Manda ummaara qini fiqu fiqumma datinoo marifana anee minakinaana qini amiqimma qimaqaananoo.
\q1 Qini namuqaauqa aanoo qiafana aneenna afeekannai misa nindaqaa qimarianafa mariananoo.
\q1 
\v 8 Anee aiqama ainaina qima afeekaikamma qoonnandee innaranoo.
\q1 Oo Yaawee ani amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
\q1 Anee maasa Isaraee maqanaasara dadaaqiraree qunnana sia qaunusee minnisaa.
\c 139
\s1 Anutufa innisaimbaqara amiqimmasee iriseenoo amiqimmasee rakisidanoo.
\q1 
\v 1 Oo Yaawee anee qini qimuqusaki diuqummaseenana qiniara irimariananoo.
\q1 
\v 2 Qini ooqu marirana faqa findifirana faqa aiqama ainaina auqee marunnanara faqa anee irimariananoo.
\q1 Anee nianaindari qini
\q1 Anee nianaindari qini qitikurakin
\q1 Anee nianaindari qini qitikurakinaa
\q1 Anee nianaindari qini qitikurakinaa iriranara irimariananoo.
\q1 
\v 3 Anee qinee ainaini marunnana faqa idooee marunnana faqa diuqimariananoo.
\q1 Anee qinee aiqama ainaina auqee marunnanara irimariananoo.
\q1 
\v 4 Oo Yaawee qinee moo ufa qianeerunana anee faasai mi ufana aiqama irimarianafa mariananoo.
\q1 
\v 5 Anee qini fiqu fiqu ina datina aiqamatinai mariananoo.
\q1 Anee aneenna afeekannai qini itita qimaqee mariananoo.
\q1 
\v 6 Ani qiniara irirafa kaaqa firaafa uriqaranoo maridanoo.
\q1 Ani mi irirafa qini irirana faqa fiaaqaranoo maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 7 Qinee ani Yaaweena maraquna minnisee yaifee moosaa fuanauree.
\q1 Qinee ani afu saaqari yaifee moosaa fuanauree.
\q1 
\v 8 Qinee innaarunai ooru firaree qianana anee minni faqa marinnaranoo.
\q1 Qinee kuqirausa mariannai firaree qianana anee minni faqa marinnaranoo.
\q1 
\v 9 Qinee qaqamaree suani afu ururee marina ooqiaaqarama fuanana anee minni faqa marinnaranoo. Suani keeqee marina fiaaqaraanana anee miqoo faqa marinnaranoo.
\q1 
\v 10 Qinee mitinai marianana anee miqoo maridana qini aana muqunimma qisarara faqa miqoo marinnaranoo.
\q1 
\v 11-12 Qinee asukunara kukeeqa qimaqaannee qimasee kaaqa qarafa qini fiqu fiqu inoo marifa quandaki asukunaikiannee qiananoo asukuna fannoo sia ani afusaa asukunara foora maridanoo.
\q1 Asukuna fannoo faasaanara foora kaaqa qaannoo.
\q1 Asukuna faqa kaaqa qarafa faqa ani afusaa amana amana kai maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 13 Anee Yaaweefa kai qini daundurakinaa ainaina aiqama auqunafa mariananoo.
\q1 Anee qini qinoona aranandaki qini qifaaqa moodaanaki ootupama qisaananoo.
\q1 
\v 14 Aniara rufiee mariafa mariannanara ani amooqidaqa.
\q1 Anee aiqama ainaina auqee marianafa mookira ainaina naaquqara ainaina auqee marianafa mariananoo.
\q1 Qinee minara qeeqa aiqama qimuqusannoo iridaqa.
\q1 
\v 15 Qini qimudaani moodaanaki ootupee marufana anee ireeda qini qinoona aranandaki moodaanaki quqaqisanau.
\q1 Qinee miqoo kukeeqaranaki innooqee mariafanana anee qinee mariafannanara iri marinau.
\q1 
\v 16 Anee sia kambiqaqa mariafana qiqafanau.
\q1 Qinee naaru moodaa moodaa faasaana auqaanna ainainara ani papiqaki akara rinoo maridanoo.
\q1 Mi moodaa moodaa faasaanafa sia kambiqanoo marufanoo miqoo ani papiqaki akararinoo maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 17 Oo Anutu ani iriranara irunanoo firaaqoo ummaara darinoo.
\q1 Moomoo uqanna maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 18 Qinee asaana ruananoo nukuda faqa arusee fiqaranoo mariannoo.
\q1 Qinee faiqaqee marii findi fiqa ani mi iriranara kaqi kai irimaree fidaqa.
\q1 
\v 19 Oo Anutu anee mandoosana maree mariasa narinnaranoo fee qidaqa.
\q1 Faiqí fidika ruqiqee mariasa qini quqasee fififaqa qeeqaraa marianauree qidaqa.
\q1 
\v 20 Misa manda ufa ani qimamaqaidaqa.
\q1 Misa oosana oosana manda ufa ani auquara qidaqa.
\q1 
\v 21 Oo Yaawee aniara fidiaqaa imariasa qinee misa fidiqaqmma nimaqaidaqa.
\q1 Ani ufamau firanara ititammasee aanoo qimariasara qinee firaaqoo qikooqaidanoo.
\q1 
\v 22 Qinee miqimariasara kaifaa firaaqoo uqanna fidiaqaamma nimaqaidaqa.
\q1 Qinee misara qini namuqaauqee qidaqa miqidaqa.
\q1 
\v 23 Oo Anutu qini diuqummasee qini iriranara iria.
\q1 Anee qini qimanammasee qini irirana oosanara iria.
\q1 
\v 24 Qini daunduraki manda ainaina qafamaseenana naaru marira aanaindari qinisaa rakisiqisaa.
\c 140
\s1 Isaraee maqannaasa Anutufa dadaaqiani fee quu ufafa.
\q1 
\v 1 Oo Yaawee mandoosana maree mariasa nisaukukinaana qini maraquqisaa.
\q1 Faiqí nariqanuasasaa faqa ititaqisaa.
\q1 
\v 2 Misa aiqama kari mandainainara tupundaaridaqa.
\q1 Misa aiqama kari aanoo qirana kai uqeeraidaqa.
\q1 
\v 3 Misa nifauru nimaakiri kuqimaria sakanifara foora maridanoo.
\q1 Misa nookinaa ufa fannoo ukadiqa manda marasinnara foora maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 4 Oo Yaawee manda oosana maree mariasa afeeka ameemaanaindaraana qini ititaqisaa.
\q1 Faiqí nariqanuasa qini qiku qama qimifaqa aqufuaneera misa tipundaridaqa.
\q1 Minara anee misa saa ititaqisaa.
\q1 
\v 5 Nári nimoo naamoo imariasa qini qimaara ufaanara foora fufidaqa.
\q1 Misa nári ufaana aatataa qini qimaara fufidaqa.
\q1 
\v 6 Oo Yaawee qinee maaqi qimasee aniara qidaqa.
\q1 Anee qini Anutufa mariananoo.
\q1 Oo Yaawee anee qini dadaaqianneera aaree marunnana iria.
\q1 
\v 7 Oo qini uriqarara Yaaweefa, anee qini amudaanai qimasee itita qimaqee marianafa mariananoo.
\q1 Rakiranaki anee qini ititaqimaqaananoo.
\q1 
\v 8 Oo Yaawee sia anee mandoosana maree mariasa nidi mari ainaina nimia.
\q1 Anee misa tipundaarirana ititannisainanoo sia anoonaikiani.
\q1 
\v 9 Anee qinaqa qini namuqaauqa sia rakiranaki uriqaraaqa.
\q1 Anee qinanoo misa darirari maria ufafa quandaki nariqa naruani.
\q1 
\v 10 Miqi mariasasaa fidika arira ida auru adia nimaqaa.
\q1 Misa dikaandaki aqusaina sia kaifaa minakiqari uruaqa.
\q1 
\v 11 Niqoonausara unna qimasee misa kikiqusi mariasa aiqama ainainirafa sia anoonaikiani.
\q1 Mandainaina fannoo faiqí kuqa nariqanuasa rafaaqafuseenoo mandaikamma nimaqaani.
\q1 
\v 12 Oo Yaawee anee kudi fasiqa anaasee kootaki itita nimaqaannanara qinee iridaqa.
\q1 Anee sarau imariasa amana amana kai itita nimaqaannanara faqa iridaqa.
\q1 
\v 13 Andeeqarausa kuqaa uqanna ani amooqifaranoo.
\q1 Misa ani afusaa marifaranoo.
\c 141
\s1 Eendaki innaaru.
\q1 
\v 1 Oo Yaawee qinee ani aaraidaqa qini maqee dadaaqia.
\q1 Qinee ani aaraanana iria.
\q1 
\v 2 Qini innaaru qirana amiqira afundimari ida munanara foora maraa.
\q1 Qinee qisauku uqeerasee innaaru qirana eeneemari suqee maria tatufiranara foora maraa.
\q1 
\v 3 Oo Yaawee anee qini doosaa rakisianinna quqasainanoo rakisi marinanoo qini dookiqari sia manda ufa ururaani.
\q1 
\v 4 Qini mandainaina auqarara didi marina ititaqisaa.
\q1 Manda fasiqauqaki ootupamafi misa manda oosana mararanasaa ititaqisaa.
\q1 Qinee sia misa qoomaqa dadaaqi naanaura.
\q1 
\v 5 Andeeqara fasiqa fannoo qini aaqarana akiiqara qini dadaaqianifee aupurarana qiminaqa qinee minara qini amiqi amiqimmidanoo fee qianaura.
\q1 Aaqee mariasa qiniara uriqarara fee qifaqa qimooqirana sia maraanaura.
\q1 Qinee maqee maqee misa manda oosannara taikaannee qimasee innaaru qimarunnanara misa qimooqirana sia maraanaura.
\q1 
\v 6 Andeeqara uriqararausa manda oosana maree mariasa misa uriqararausa rafuseeqee maaninni aqusaifaqa faiqí anaasee qini ufara kuqaa anoonee qifaranoo.
\q1 
\v 7 Mi manda uriqararausa nimudaani saqari araira foora moomoo madika afaiqara irairaa inoo mariannoo.
\q1 
\v 8 Oo Uriqarara Yaawee qinee kaqi ani saqarikidaqa.
\q1 Qinee ani itita imaqaranara randaidaqa.
\q1 Anee qiniara qaoo qinaqa sia kuquanaura.
\q1 
\v 9 Qini qimaara qinukufana fufuqaanasaa ititaqisaa.
\q1 Manda oosana maree mariasa qiku ufana fufuqaanasaa ititaqisaa.
\q1 
\v 10 Manda oosana maree mariasa nariqa ufaanaki aru fifaqa qinee amiqimmasee fuanaura sia minaki aruanaura.
\c 142
\s1 Dadaaqiani fee innaaru.
\q1 
\v 1 Qinee dadaaqianifeera Yaaweena aaraidaqa.
\q1 Qinee qiki raqaidaqa minara innaaru qidaqa.
\q1 
\v 2 Qinee qeeqa aiqama inunu rira ufauqa mina amidaqa.
\q1 Qinee qeeqa aiqama ummaara mina qimamidaqa.
\q1 
\v 3 Qinee minnisara runanoo qinee andeeqasee qianna ainnainnara mifa iridanoo.
\q1 Qinee fimarunna aannanasaa qini namuqaa qini qimaara kukeeqasee ufaana fufidaqa.
\q1 
\v 4 Qinee qeeqa inaaqiannai dadaaqiranara qafaunanoo sia maridanoo.
\q1 Sia moo fannoo qini ititaqimaqaaninafa maridanoo.
\q1 Sia moo fannoo qiniara qimudaoo qidanoo.
\q1 
\v 5 Oo Yaawee anee dadaaqianneera aaraidaqa.
\q1 Anee Yaaweefa qini itita qimaqee marianafa mariananoo.
\q1 Maa maqanasaa mariranaki maridaqa aniara kai ridaqa.
\q1 
\v 6 Oo Yaawee qinee dadaaqianneera qiki raqee marunnana iria.
\q1 Manda ummaara fannoo qini nammariara foora ukuqnama saifaqa kuqiraridaqa.
\q1 Qini namuqaa kaaqa afeeka faqaasa marianara qini misa nisaukukinaana mara kaqinni quqaqisaa.
\q1 
\v 7 Qini teerookinaana iduku qisainaqa ani faiqí anaasee suqiranaki ani amooqianaura.
\q1 Anee qini amiqimma qimaqaannanara ani amooqianaura.
\c 143
\s1 Dadaaqiani fee innaaru.
\q1 
\v 1 Oo Yaawee qini innaaruqirana iria.
\q1 Aneenna andeeqaranakiqari qini afeeka innaaruqirana iria.
\q1 Aneenna mapukira oosanakiqari qini ufa anoona qima qimia.
\q1 
\v 2 Sia moo fannoo maa maqanasaa qaraafa ani afusaa andeeqarafa maridaqa.
\q1 Minara anee sia qini aneenna ainainira fasiqa mareeqee aneenna kootaki quqasee qimanammasee qafaa.
\q1 
\v 3 Qini namuqaa qini qifaqasee firaaqoo uqanna qini rafaaqa fidaqa.
\q1 Mifa qini asukuna rumbaranaki quqasaifaqa qinee ooqai kuqusara foora maridaqa.
\q1 
\v 4 Miqimmasaifaqa qinee minnisarara deedaqidaqa.
\q1 Qini qimuqusa fannoo munara minari marifaqa kaaqa kuquaqaa idaqa.
\q1 
\v 5 Qinee indaaru mariaafanna mariranara oonu mafi iridaqa.
\q1 Qinee anee aiqama ainaina iannanara iridaqa.
\q1 Anee aiqama ainaina auqaannanara qeeqa iriranaki minisee iridaqa.
\q1 
\v 6 Qinee innaarukiqari qeeqa qisauku anee iannannai uqeeraidaqa.
\q1 Aadana maqara foora qini qimana fannoo aniara nammariara foora aididanoo.
\q1 
\v 7 Oo Yaawee qini marirafa taikaaqaammidanoo.
\q1 Qini ufa irisee mina anoona qimaqimia.
\q1 Sia qini qiqafamasee kukeeqaa.
\q1 Anee miqinaqa qinee kuqirausa fimariannai fuanaura.
\q1 
\v 8 Aiqama kananaana anee daaqoo auqainaqa ani sia taikaaninna amuqusiranara irisee qeeqa saqarikirana aniki quqaanaura.
\q1 Qini innaaru qirafa anee iannannai ooru fidanoo.
\q1 Anee qiniara fuannee qinnaqoo uqaqifiqainaqa fua.
\q1 
\v 9 Oo Yaawee ititaqimaqaanneera anee iannannai fidaqa.
\q1 Qini namuqaa nisaukukinaana mara kaqinni quqaqisaa.
\q1 
\v 10 Anee qini Anutufa mariannanara aneenna aidira ainaina qima qiminaqa auqaa.
\q1 Qini amiqimma qisaseenana amiqira aanasaa ititaqimaqainaqa fua.
\q1 
\v 11 Oo Yaawee aneenna qima afeekaikunandee inana qini namuqaa nisaukukinaana maraqu qisaa.
\q1 Aneenna andeeqaranakiqari qini ummaarakinaana mara quqaqisaa.
\q1 
\v 12 Anee qiniara aidi mariannanara qini namuqaa kuqa narua.
\q1 Qinee ani ainainira fasiqa marunnanara nári uriqararanannai qini rafaaqafi mariasa aiqama kuridi nimaqaa.
\c 144
\s1 Davidifa rakirana uriaaqaroonara Anutunara dufi dufi qinau.
\q1 
\v 1 Qini itita qimaqee marina Yaaweena amooqia.
\q1 Mifa rakira oosana uqaqifiqaseenoo qini rakiranaki firana deedaqamma qisaidanoo.
\q1 
\v 2 Mifa qini aiqama kari itita qimaqee marifa maridanoo.
\q1 Mifa qini auqaanara foora qini asumu maree marifa maridanoo.
\q1 Qini amiqimma qisaanifeera mina saqarikidaqa.
\q1 Mifa faiqí anaasee mareeqeenoo qini qiramandunnai quqaidanoo.
\q1 
\v 3 Oo Yaawee faiqí anaasee nana ainainee mariafanee anee misara iridanee.
\q1 Faiqí anaasee nana ainainee fifau ainaina mariafanee anee misa rakisi nimaqaidanee.
\q1 
\v 4 Faiqí misa naidoora foora fuaqasaafanoo dauni taikeera foora irausa maridaqa.
\q1 Mina marirafa nimanandara foora kaqi kaqi mandaaqee marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 5 Oo Yaawee anee innaaruna rakee maseenana qumureenana aaqanauqa auqamasainanoo ida muna minakiqari ururaani.
\q1 
\v 6 Miqimmaseenana aneenna aakuasaa panana qirana quqasainanoo qumureenoo ani namuqaauqa furu faramma nimaqaannoo.
\q1 Aakuasaa aneenna feefara foora dindai qinaqa quqasee sandaaqa.
\q1 
\v 7 Oo Yaawee anee innaarunaindari qini mara miami anaamuru nisaukuki nammari faruma kiara foora marunnana uqeereeqee kaqinni quqaqisaa.
\q1 Anaamuru afeeka ameemaanai marunnana mareeqee kaqinni quqaqisaa.
\q1 
\v 8 Mi anaamurusa nifaurusaa unnufa kai qumbiqanoo marifaqa misa kuqaa ufa qiraree qimasee nimana aiqamasee unna ufa kai qidaqa.
\q1 
\v 9 Oo Anutu qinee aniara fuka idi ramamaqaanaura.
\q1 Qinee piripunna aridaqa ani idi ramama qaanaura.
\q1 
\v 10 Anee kai karaambaiqauqa rakirana uriqarara afeeka nimimarianafa mariananoo.
\q1 Anee aneenna ainainira fasiqa qini Davidisa namuqaa nisaukukinaana maree marianafa mariananoo.
\q1 
\v 11 Anee fitiqnarana qimi maria namuqaasa nisaukuki marunnana anee mara kaqinni quqaqisaa.
\q1 Anaamuru afeeka ameemaanai marunnana mara kaqinni quqaqisaa.
\q1 Mi anaamurusa nifaurusaa unna ufa kai qumbiqanoo maridanoo.
\q1 Misa kuqaa ufa qiraree qimasee nimana aiqamasee unnufa kai qidaqa.
\q1 
\v 12 Maasa faiqi namu aanaaqisaaqari findifiqa ummaqira saqariara foora afeekaikammasee ururaaqa.
\q1 Maasa qiraamuqmaaka faqa maqasaa karaambaiqa maaqakina amiqira afaaqa auqira sapatariara foora maridaqa maasa asasirana qimiaqa.
\q1 
\v 13 Maasa afeedira maaqaki oosana oosana nara ainaina qumbiqanoo mariani.
\q1 Maasa maaqeena aandau sia kasoo anaaqiuqa uqanna maqaaqa.
\q1 
\v 14 Maasa maaqeena aandauqa kaifaa moomoo kiqa faiqi maqasaifanoo sia eedadaikinaqa kuquaqa.
\q1 Maasa maqusaki sia teeroo faqa qiki raqarafa faqa mariani.
\q1 
\v 15 Miqi maria fasiqa anaaseesa amiqiranaki asasiranaki marifaranoo.
\q1 Yaaweefa maasa Anutufa marifaqee qimaria fasiqa aanaaseesa asasiranaki maridaqa.
\c 145
\s1 Anutuna amooqira idi.
\q1 
\v 1 Qini Anutu qini Karaambaiqa, qinee anee uriqararafa mariannanara kooroo ianaura.
\q1 Qinee ani naaruara naaruara dufi dufi amooqianaura.
\q1 
\v 2 Aiqama kari ani dufi dufi qimamaqaanaura.
\q1 Qinee naaruara naaruara ani amooqianaura.
\q1 
\v 3 Yaaweefa uriqararafa marifaqa mina uriqaramasee amooqi mariafa maridanoo.
\q1 Mina uriqararafa firaafa irirafa munu taikarana fiqaranoo maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 4 Anee auqoonna ainainnara maqee mariasa faqa naaru kambiqainausa faqa ani amooqifaranoo.
\q1 Misa anee auqoonna afeeka ainainnara kooroo ifaranoo.
\q1 
\v 5 Misa ani qareenaranara faqa ani afeekara faqa ufa qifaranoo.
\q1 Qinee ani naaquqara ainaina auquqoonnanara maqee maqee indee indee iqa fuanaura.
\q1 
\v 6 Faiqí anaasee afeeka ainaina anee auqee mariannanara ufa qimariafaqa qinee ani uriqararanara kooroo ianaura.
\q1 
\v 7 Misa ani andeeqaranara qima nimisee ani amiqi amiqiranara idi reefaranoo.
\q1 
\v 8 Yaaweefa aidi marifanoo nifauaidanoo.
\q1 Mina aranaqarafa kasooaqee kasooaqee qimarifanoo mina sia taikaaninna amuqusirafa qumbiqaidanoo.
\q1 
\v 9 Mifa aiqamausa amiqi amiqimma nimaqaseenoo narí aiqama auqu quqaqoo ainainausara amuqusi marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 10 Oo Yaawee anee aiqama aandau doodaani auquqoonausa ani amooqifaqa aiqama ani faiqí anaasee dufi dufi qirana ani amifaranoo.
\q1 
\v 11 Misa ani karaambaiqa afeeka areenaranara ufa qidaqa ani amudaanai qiranara qifaranoo.
\q1 
\v 12 Miqimmasaifaqa aiqamausa anee afeeka ainaina auqoonnanara irifaranoo.
\q1 Misa ani afeeka areenara ququsara faqa irifarannoo.
\q1 
\v 13 Ani rakisi nimaqarafa naaru naaru marifa marifana anee naaruara karaambaiqa mariananoo.
\q1 Yaaweefa narí qima afeekaika maqoo ufanasaa mapukinoo marifa maridanoo.
\q1 Narí aiqama ainaina imarina nifauarana namu faqa idanoo.
\q1 
\v 14 Mifa ummaaraki mariasa dadaaqidanoo.
\q1 Mifa rafaaqafu nimaqee mariasa uqeera nisaidanoo.
\q1 
\v 15 Aiqama kasi maria ainainausa narana nimianneera nifu mundusee ani kai qafaafana narana nimi mariananoo.
\q1 
\v 16 Anee misa nimana kai niminana aiqamausa nidirana amanaikiananoo.
\q1 
\v 17 Yaaweena aiqama ainaina auqaranaki andeeqarafa maridanoo.
\q1 Narí aiqama ainaina imarina nifauarana namu faqa idanoo.
\q1 
\v 18 Mifa narí aaree mariasa naaqa maridanoo.
\q1 Mifa nariqa nimuqusa ookiqari aaree mariasa naaqa faqa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 19 Mifa nariara naaquqee marifaqa mina ufa qaindusi mariasa dadaaqira ainainauqa nimidanoo.
\q1 Mifa misa qiki raqarana iriseenoo misa ummaarakinaana mara kaqinni quqannisaidanoo.
\q1 
\v 20 Mifa nariara rimariasa itita nimaqasee mandoosana maree mariasa kuridi nimaqaannoo.
\q1 
\v 21 Qinee aiqama kari Yaaweena amooqianaura.
\q1 Mifa auqu aiqama ainainausa mina naaquqara andeeqara auqu naaru naaru amooqima amaqaaqa.
\c 146
\s1 Dadaaqira fasiqa Anutuna amooqia.
\q1 
\v 1 Yaaweena amooqia.
\q1 Oo qini qimana Yaaweena amooqia.
\q1 
\v 2 Qinee kaqi marunna kamuqoo Yaaweena amooqianaura.
\q1 Qeeqa aiqama kari maa maqa maaqanasaa mariranaki qeeqa Anutuna idi ramamaqaanaura.
\q1 
\v 3 Sia aneenna saqarikirana maqasaa qaraa uriqararausasaa quqaa.
\q1 Sia faiqí faiqi amana ani dadaaqiannoo.
\q1 
\v 4 Maqasaa uriqararausa kuqufiqa kookoommaika mafidaqa.
\q1 Mi faasaannasaa misa oosana oosana ainainara tipundaarammaqaafa taikaidanoo.
\q1 
\v 5 Yakooboona Anutunara dadaaqirana qimiannee qimari fasiqafa faqa Yaaweena nariqa Anutunasaa mundi mariasa faqa asasidaqa.
\q1 
\v 6 Innaaruna faqa maqa faqa ooruku nammari faqa minaki maria ainainausa faqa auqunasaa mundi mariasa asasidaqa.
\q1 Mifa aiqama kari narí qima afeekaikiranasaa afu rusisee maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 7 Mifa uriqararanannai rafaaqa fuqaasa narí ufa iriranaki dadaaqidanoo.
\q1 Naararee mariasa faa narana nimidanoo.
\q1 Yaaweefa fifau rumbaranaki mariasa iduku nisaidanoo.
\q1 
\v 8 Iduku nisaseenoo nifu imbarausa nifu maqa nisaidanoo.
\q1 Mifa aqufiqa mariasa uqeera nisaidanoo.
\q1 Mifa narí andeeqara fasiqa aanaaseera aididanoo.
\q1 
\v 9 Yaaweefa asaqiraafai maasa maqa maaqaki mariasasaa itita nimaqaidanoo.
\q1 Mifa adeedaana anaaseeuqa faqa fiaiqi faiqiuqa faqa dadaaqidanoo.
\q1 Kafaa mifa manda oosana maree mariasa nariqa kuridiranaki quqa nisaidanoo.
\q1 
\v 10 Yaaweefa naaruara uriqararafa maridanoo.
\q1 Oo Sioona maqusa ani Anutufa aiqama kari rakisi amaqaannoo.
\q1 Yaaweena amooqia.
\c 147
\s1 Anutuna aiqama afeeka faqaana amooqia.
\q1 
\v 1 Yaaweena amooqia.
\q1 Maasa Anutuna amooqira idi rarafa amiqira oosana maridanoo.
\q1 Mina amooqirafa andeeqarafa adiafaairafa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 2 Yaaweefa Yeerusaree maqusa kaifaa usakaidanoo.
\q1 Isaraee maqannaasa narufaqa anaamurukiaqa moodaa moodaa iqa mariusa Yaaweefa kafaa suqeeqee quqaidanoo.
\q1 
\v 3 Mifa nimuqusa mandaiki marusa amiqimma nisaidanoo.
\q1 Misa kaakadi narirana rumbannisaidanoo.
\q1 
\v 4 Mifa aiqama fasauqara iriseenoo asaana rirana amana kai quqaseenoo naadu naadu nuqu ranau.
\q1 
\v 5 Maasa Yaaweefa firaafa marida amudaanai qimarifa maridanoo.
\q1 Mina amiqira irirafa sia oosana faqa ammuqu faqa marifa maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 6 Mifa nári mara maree qumi mariasa uqeerannisaidanoo.
\q1 Kafaa mandoosana maree mariasa maqa mammaaqai radamidanoo.
\q1 
\v 7 Amooqira idi Yaaweenara rama amaqaaqa.
\q1 Piripunannai aridaqa maasa Anutuna idi rama amaqaaqa.
\q1 
\v 8 Mifa oonnamu innaarunai rainaidanoo.
\q1 Mifa aaku quqasaifanoo rifanoo amuaqu namusaaqaraa andandauqa ururaidanoo.
\q1 
\v 9 Mifa aandauqa narana nimisee ufini aanaaqiuqa naranara qiafanoo misa faqa nimidanoo.
\q1 
\v 10 Mifa qoosauqa afeekara sia ridanoo.
\q1 Mifa afeeka sundiauqa rakiranaki paasoosi mariasa afeekara faqa sia ridanoo.
\q1 
\v 11 Mifa nariara naaquqaifaqa rufiee mariasara aididanoo.
\q1 Misa nári irirana Yaaweena sia taikaaninna amuqusiranasaa rusimariasa misara aididanoo.
\q1 
\v 12 Oo Yeerusaree maqusaki mariasa innee Yaaweena amooqiaqa.
\q1 Oo Sioona maqusaki mariasa inneeqa Anutuna kai amooqiaqa.
\q1 
\v 13 Mifa inni maqusa faandaamura kooqi afeekaikammasee ititaidanoo.
\q1 Mifa minaki maria fasiqa anaaseesa amiqi amiqimma nimaqaidanoo.
\q1 
\v 14 Mifa inni Isaraee maqannaa oosusaa rakisidanoo amiqira narana inni nimana kai nimidanoo.
\q1 
\v 15 Mifa narí naamuaqira ufa maa maqana qimamisaifanoo mifa qii ainainafa kai kaqi kambiqaidanoo.
\q1 
\v 16 Mifa qaisara qifanoo aqufinoo qamunnara foora maqasaa rafaaqa fidanoo.
\q1 
\v 17 Mifa innaarunaindari pupusamu oonisamuara foora aqidanoo.
\q1 Sia moo fannoo mifa nimi mari suaranaki amana kikiqiannoo.
\q1 
\v 18 Mifa pupusamuara qifanoo tasirisirinoo nammarikidanoo.
\q1 Kafaa mifa ufaira qufanoo ufai uqufanoo qaisa fannoo firaa nammari kammafi ooqu finau.
\q1 
\v 19 Mifa narí ufa narí faiqí anaasee nimidanoo.
\q1 Mifa narí sandufa faqa narí naakaparufa faqa Isaraee maqannaasa nimidanoo.
\q1 
\v 20 Mifa mi ainainna auqoona sia moo maqannaasa mina sanda ufa sia iri mariasarau auqinoo fau.
\q1 Yaaweena amooqia.
\c 148
\s1 Aiqama innaarunaindaraa ainaina faqa maqasaaqaraa ainaina faqa Anutuna amooqidaqa.
\q1 
\v 1 Yaaweena amooqia.
\q1 Innaarunai mirinni mariasa Yaaweena amooqiaqa.
\q1 
\v 2 Mina aiqama qangeeroouqa mina innaarunaindaraa rakira fasiqauqa mina amooqiaqa.
\q1 
\v 3 Innee suani faqa quqoona faqa aiqama fasau firaaqoo kaaqa qeemariasa faqa aiqama mina amooqiaqa.
\q1 
\v 4 Innaaruna meerai uqanna marianafa anee faqa Yaaweena amooqia.
\q1 Innee mirinni innaarunai maria nammarisa innee faqa mina kai amooqiaqa.
\q1 
\v 5 Misa aiqamausa Yaaweena amooqiaqanani.
\q1 Mifa qufaqa misa kambiqaqau.
\q1 
\v 6 Mina ufannoo misa kambiqafi nariqa mariaqoo naaru naaru maridaqa sia amana Yaaweena ufa rukieefaranoo.
\q1 
\v 7-8 Maqasaaqaraa ainainauqa faqa ooruku nammariki maria firaa aandausa faqa nammari ameemaanai mariasa faqa aakuasaa faqa pupusamu faqa qaisa faqa oonnamu faqa afeeka ufai Yaaweena naakapara ufa mau fimari ufaifa faqa innee aiqamausa Yaaweena amooqiaqa.
\q1 
\v 9-10 Innee aaqanauqa faqa amuaqu namuqa faqa qaqama iree maria saqarisa faqa aiqama nandauqa faqa aiqama aandau maaqeena faqa kaasau faqa nimuaqundari nimariasa faqa qaqamaree nimaria ufinisa faqa innee aiqama mina amooqima amaqaaqa.
\q1 
\v 11-12 Aiqama maqasaaqaraa karaambaiqauqa faqa aiqama maqannaasa faqa uriqararausa faiqi namu faqa aiqama maqannaa rakisirausa faqa kumaaraauqa faqa maanaaqauqa faqa asooqa fasiqa anaasee faqa faiqi uqaindi faqa innee aiqamausa Yaaweena amooqiaqa.
\q1 
\v 13 Misa aiqama misoo maasoo Yaaweena auqu amooqiaqa. Mina auqu fannoo aiqamausa nuqu uriqararafa maridanoo.
\q1 Mina areenarafa maa maqa maaqana faqa innaaruna faqa urinaaqaranoo maridanoo.
\q1 
\v 14 Mifa Yaaweefa narí maqannaasa afeekaikamma nisaifaqa mina faiqi anaasee mina amooqiaqeera.
\q1 Isaraee maqannaasa mina afaaqasaa aqoondiuqa maridaqa mina amooqidaqa.
\q1 Yaaweena amooqia.
\c 149
\s1 Anutuna amooqira idi.
\q1 
\v 1 Yaaweena amooqia.
\q1 Yaaweena fuka idi ramamaqaaqa.
\q1 Mina ufa mau fimariasa ufa suqiranaki mina amooqimamaqaaqa.
\q1 
\v 2 Isaraee maqannaasa inni auqu nisoonara irisee asasiaqa.
\q1 Sioona maqusaki mariasa inneeqa karaambaiqara susumma amaqaaqa.
\q1 
\v 3 Innee idi raida niqoori raqaranannai faqa dukaanaannai faqa piripunnannai faqa mina auqu amooqiaqa.
\q1 
\v 4 Yaaweefa narí faiqí aanaaseera asasidanoo.
\q1 Nári mara maree qumimariasa rakirana uriqararanannai amiqimma nimaqaidanoo.
\q1 
\v 5 Yaaweena faiqí anaasee nariqa rakiranara qufoonaridaqa asasira idi eendaki raqa fifi iaqaaqa.
\q1 
\v 6 Misa firaaqoo faaq rumasee Anutuna amooqiaqa.
\q1 Misa nisaukuki dinni dinni raiqarana rakira paipana kaqi marinaqa mina namu faqa amooqiaqa.
\q1 
\v 7 Kaqi marifaqa misa minannai aanaamuru rafaaqa firara uaqee idaqa.
\q1 Anaamuru fasiqa anaasee narirara uaqee idaqa.
\q1 
\v 8 Misa karaambaiqauqa sainandannai rumbarana uaqee idaqa.
\q1 Misa karaambaiqauqa qainna sainandannai rumbarara uaqee idaqa.
\q1 
\v 9 Anutufa naamuaqundee iqa moo maqannaasa narirara uaqee idaqa.
\q1 Anutuna faiqí anaasee rakirana uriqararafa miqimminoo maridanoo.
\q1 Yaaweena amooqia.
\c 150
\s1 Yaaweena amooqia.
\q1 
\v 1 aaweena amooqia.
\q1 Anutuna naaquqara amaana maqaki mina amooqiaqa.
\q1 Mina uriqarara afeeka innaaru nai marina amooqiaqa.
\q1 
\v 2 Mifa afeeka ainaina auqoo nara amooqima amaqaaqa.
\q1 Mina amiqira uriqararanara amooqiaqa.
\q1 
\v 3 Ukeena fuaqaidaqa minannai mina amooqiaqa.
\q1 Kaqikaa piripunnannai faqa firaa piripunnannai faqa mina amooqiaqa.
\q1 
\v 4 Dukaanaannai faqa idi raida niqoori raqaranannai faqa mina amooqiaqa.
\q1 Piripunnannai faqa ufireenannai faqa mina amooqiaqa.
\q1 
\v 5 Innee qumiandau qaqama kaqikaa qanda faqa firaa qanda faqa qumaree narisaa narisaa ramoo ramoo idaqa Yaaweena amooqiaqa.
\q1 
\v 6 \fig Oosana oosana piripunna idi raidaqa arimariafa maridanoo.|alt="Group of musical instruments showing relative sizes" src="bk00174b bjr.tif" size="span" loc="Psalm 150:6" ref="150"\fig*Aiqama naanna faqaa ainaina Yaaweena amooqiaqa. Yaaweena amooqia. 
